dy offered by Word Fun. \nAlthough the basic gameplay of the Word Hunt, Word Rockets and Crosswords games appears unchanged from the original Word Fun cartridge, the graphics were enhanced. According to the official site, a bug was introduced in the Crosswords game that resulted in the computer only choosing words starting with letters A-T instead of A-Z. The new game added to the mix is Memory Fun - your basic 'Memory' style game where you turn over pairs of tiles to find matches. Another grand edutainment game. No wonder they made so many. ;-)","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[19222,41348,10225,27266,14246,60044,236,27725,101980,101976],"tags":[268435465],"category":0,"genres":[9],"first_release_date":555379200000,"platforms":[67],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":67,"date":555379200000,"region":8,"human":"1987-Aug-08","y":1987,"m":8}]},{"id":41432,"name":"Learning Fun I","slug":"learning-fun-i","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/learning-fun-i","created_at":1498817225630,"updated_at":1500268623483,"summary":"MATH MASTER: \nYou are a gorilla strolling along the banks of a river. Your path is suddenly blocked by an animal! Under the animal is a math problem. You must solve the problem correctly in order to continue your walk. \n \nFACTOR FUN: \nYou are a gorilla sitting at an adding machine. A number appears above you. This is the TARGET NUMBER. Below you appear several WHITE numbers (how many depends on the difficulty level). Your task is to add, subtract, multiply, and divide the white numbers to reach the Target Number.","popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[19222,41348,10225,27266,14246,60044,236,27725,101980,101976],"tags":[268435465],"category":0,"genres":[9],"first_release_date":539136000000,"platforms":[67],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":67,"date":539136000000,"region":8,"human":"1987-Feb-01","y":1987,"m":2}]},{"id":41433,"name":"The Jetsons' Ways with Words","slug":"the-jetsons-ways-with-words","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/t