ng game that allows the player to join any team in the 1993 Formula One season and take part on sixteen different circuits all over the world. They can also configure the load-out for the F1 vehicle. \n \nIt is the second official F1 Circus game for the system, though technically the third due to 1992's Super F1 Circus Limited. Overall it is the eighth F1 Circus game.","collection":3209,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"games":[58785,42572,38172,38171,40470,69725,48498,41649,28856,80441],"tags":[268435466,536874337,536875069,536875117,536876749],"category":0,"keywords":[3425,4157,4205,5837],"genres":[10],"first_release_date":743904000000,"platforms":[19],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":19,"date":743904000000,"region":5,"human":"1993-Jul-29","y":1993,"m":7},{"category":0,"platform":19,"date":746582400000,"region":8,"human":"1993-Aug-29","y":1993,"m":8}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/i3zi5xphg7icnunnha39.jpg","cloudinary_id":"i3zi5xphg7icnunnha39","width":384,"height":210}},{"id":42269,"name":"Super F1 Circus","slug":"super-f1-circus","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/super-f1-circus","created_at":1499071143017,"updated_at":1516722396712,"summary":"Super F1 Circus is a F1 racing game from Cream and Nichibutsu (Nihon Bussan) and the first Super Famicom entry in the F1 Circus entry, which originated on the PC Engine (Turbografx-16) and Famicom. It is sponsored by Team Lotus, a former racing company associated with Formula 1 as well as many other racing leagues that has recently come back into being. \n \nThe game is a traditional top-down racing game that emphasizes sim elements, such as selecting the car's various parts and ensuring that the rules of the race are followed. If the player causes too many infractions, or too much damage is caused to six vital instruments on the car, they will be forced out of the race. \n \nAs well as the other games in the F1 Circus series, Super F1 Circus would receive numerous direct sequels of its