 a level. They will receive a bonus for clearing the screen, however. \n \nOccasionally, items will drop from the destroyed blocks. These include extending and shrinking the paddle, adding more balls, extra lives and power stars. By collecting power stars, the player can increase the strength that the ball leaves the paddle, causing more damage to blocks. If the player finds four stars, this charged up bounce will clear the screen. \n \nSkulls can often drop from blocks too, and collecting these will lower a green gauge at the side of the screen, which operates as a combined timer/health bar.","popularity":1.0,"games":[68324,36608,47823,12632,34919,27209,36926,82853,42553,16468],"tags":[1,536871208,536875071],"category":0,"keywords":[296,4159],"themes":[1],"first_release_date":812937600000,"platforms":[19],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":19,"date":812937600000,"region":5,"human":"1995-Oct-06","y":1995,"m":10},{"category":0,"platform":19,"date":815616000000,"region":8,"human":"1995-Nov-06","y":1995,"m":11}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/qsqfdmv4dhyegd0p9fkw.jpg","cloudinary_id":"qsqfdmv4dhyegd0p9fkw","width":525,"height":943}},{"id":42325,"name":"Puzzle'n Desu","slug":"puzzlen-desu","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/puzzlen-desu","created_at":1499072347198,"updated_at":1516637565442,"summary":"A puzzle game for the Super Famicom where the hero has to push blocks across a grid to complete lines of the same color.","popularity":1.0,"games":[26223,60044,25222,14047,79094,78652,70388,66469,66392,65312],"tags":[268435465,536871208,536873787],"category":0,"keywords":[296,2875],"genres":[9],"first_release_date":797817600000,"platforms":[19],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":19,"date":797817600000,"region":5,"human":"1995-Apr-14","y":1995,"m":4}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/hkwpqfldzxz97hvdi7m4.jpg","cloudinary_id":"hkwpqfldzxz97hvdi7m4","width":640,"height":343}},{"id":42326,"name":"Great Battle