fen, and Takeo where Origins left off. \n \nCOLLECTIBLE STEELBOOK - Limited edition steel game case featuring an exclusive design. \n \nIN-GAME BONUS CONTENT: BLACK OPS 3 BONUS PACK - Join the battle with the official Black Ops III personalization pack. Pack includes a custom weapon camo, reticle, and calling card. \n \nIN-GAME BONUS CONTENT: CYBORG - The fan favorite Cyborg Personalization Pack returns in Call of Duty: Black Ops III, fully-loaded with an electrotech-themed weapon skin, uniquely-shaped reticle, and a calling card. \n \nOFFICIAL CALL OF DUTY: BLACK OPS III SOUNDTRACK - Upgrade your playlist with a digital copy of the in-game score.","collection":1956,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"version_parent":9509,"version_title":"Juggernog Edition","games":[28029,36950,25311,68287,76229,27314,23175,27523,29525,25300],"tags":[1,18,39,268435461,268435487],"category":0,"themes":[1,18,39],"genres":[5,31],"first_release_date":1449360000000,"platforms":[48],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":48,"date":1449360000000,"region":8,"human":"2015-Dec-06","y":2015,"m":12}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/redceficumk2gckccc5h.jpg","cloudinary_id":"redceficumk2gckccc5h","width":1000,"height":684}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/mgxos9e8weyndkv8urcj.jpg","cloudinary_id":"mgxos9e8weyndkv8urcj","width":1198,"height":1329}},{"id":42949,"name":"Tower of Guns Steelbook Limited Edition","slug":"tower-of-guns-steelbook-limited-edition","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/tower-of-guns-steelbook-limited-edition","created_at":1499084675065,"updated_at":1500572082447,"summary":"Ascend the Tower of Guns and return to the days of circle-strafing, rocket-jumping, and twitch-based action. Tower of Guns is a throwback first-person shooter with a healthy sprinkling of roguelike-ish-y elements. Every turn brings a surprise and around every corner lies certain death! Or a new weird item! Or a ... Hugbot? Filled with random leve